\cf1\b\i Program Runner\cf0\i0  \b0 is an utility that helps you to run any external program, without write any Code!!\line By just 1 click, \cf1\b\i Program Runner\i0   \cf0\b0 creates a proper dedicated script, that fires-up the program you wanted. Any!! From Word to Excel, to Chrome, to MP3TAG, to DDP_to_CUE, to any ...\par
The created script is automatically loaded/imported into the Action List, and it will be always available to you.\par
You can assign it to a button on a toolbar, or to any menu (the Main one as well as a contextual one and so on).\par
It turns this operation from \i nerdy \i0 to \b user friendly one\b0\par
UltraSchall ReaPack Library is manatory: https://github.com/Ultraschall/ultraschall-lua-api-for-reaper/raw/master/ultraschall_api_index.xml\par
